intervention.description:
Bundle of evidence-based interventions that include the following 5 components:
Community engagement meetings and feedback;
Elimination of public sector facility user fees for children under five and pregnant women;
Pro-active community based IMCI using trained, equipped, supervised, and salaried Community Health Workers (CHWs) with additional services including linkage to family planning and counseling, HIV testing & referrals;
Clinical mentoring and enhanced supervision by a trained peer coach at public sector facilities;
Basic infrastructure improvements and supply chain management training of pharmacy managers
